            "description": "The ability to prepare and submit reports to a regulatory body, either voluntarily or in line with regulations on deals, positions and risk associated with trading activities. The scope of this function is mutually exclusive to regulatory reporting functions that sits within corporate functions - Risk, Finance and Treasury",
            "parentId": 62968,
