                    "name": "Transaction Regulatory Reporting Controls",
                    "description": "Transaction Regulatory Reporting Controls focus on ensuring timelines, accuracy and completeness of reports to the regulator, this capability also covers the handling of exceptions (both internally and externally) as well as data replays.",
