                    "description": "Transaction Regulatory Report Distribution involves the distribution of the report to the regulator, in the majority of cases this involves DB publishing data but can also include the regulator calling DB API's to source data directly. Reporting frequency can vary from near-real-time reporting all the way through to end of Month / end of Year requirements.",
