                            "description": "Reputational Risk Management: The following key high level services are provided:\n- Design, set and maintain the Reputational Risk Framework including policies / minimum standards\n- Establish the Reputational Risk framework and policies\n- Determine risk tolerance for the organization in relation to reputational risk on certain topics\n- Identify and implement rep risk management tools\n- Coordinate the sharing of risk knowledge across the organization and provide training\n- Reputational risk look-back process\n- Advisory services regarding the rep risk governance processes\n- Reporting for external disclosures e.g. NFR Report, Annual Report, Pillar III\n- Reporting for internal purposes e.g. monthy RCP report, regional reports, legal entity reports\nThe following key high level services are provided in relation to business activities in the defence , gaming and adult sectors:\n- Identify risks and set due diligence requirements and risk appetite, documenting with policies and procedures \n- Assess and opine on the reputational risks, referring to the relevant rep risk fora as applicable\n- Ongoing reputational risk monitoring / mitigations",
