                    "description": "Represents contractual agreement between the Bank and customer legal entity outlining the terms and conditions of research services the bank offers. \r\nSchedule attached to the legal Research Services Agreement (RSA) called Product Service Addendum (PSA)  outlines products and services which particular client wishes to use and pay for. It also lists number of user licenses available to the client for subscription purposes. In simple terms this is similar to a magazine subscription, which entitles customer to access issues of that magazine. Entitlement can also give client's personnel access to interact with particular analyst or group of analysts which also drives to billable revenue.",
